WEBVTT

00:04:01.316 --> 00:04:04.530
And in fact, if you're not really careful,

00:04:04.554 --> 00:04:10.165
you get people's minds thinking much more
about failure prevention

00:04:10.189 --> 00:04:11.625
than about soaring.

00:04:12.023 --> 00:04:13.221
No one has ever excelled

00:04:13.245 --> 00:04:16.380
because they stopped making
grammatical errors in their writing.

00:04:16.404 --> 00:04:19.189
